  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Formwork Supervisor:</strong></p><p>-Knowledge and skills to supervise formwork activities which\ninclude the construction, erection, alteration or dismantling and inspection of\nformwork structures at any worksite.</p><p>-Formwork Construction Course/Formwork Safety Course</p><p>-Knowledge and skills on application of the fundamentals of\nformwork and falsework structure construction</p><p>-Knowledge on Codes of Practice on Construction, Erection,\nAlteration or Dismantling of any formwork structure at a worksite</p><p>-Risk Assessment for formwork activities<br />\n-Interpretation of working drawings<br />\n-Construction strength of materials and shoring<br />\n-Inspection of formwork and falsework structure before, during and after\nconcreting</p>",
